{"tid":1946792,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"英國首席醫療官克里斯惠蒂報稱有病徵　正在家中自我隔離","createTime":"2020-03-28T00:08:23.000Z","updateTime":"2020-03-28T01:44:47.000Z","uid":79563,"like":2,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"1e439743e2308e1eb481d0cb96077aedf9d482c2","tid":1946792,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-28T00:08:23.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://newsstatic.rthk.hk/images/mfile_1517342_1_L_20200328013315.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnewsstatic.rthk.hk%2Fimages%2Fmfile_1517342_1_L_20200328013315.jpg&h=8b6d1f43&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n英國繼續抗擊新型冠狀病毒疫情。首席醫療官克里斯惠蒂報稱有病徵，正進行自我隔離。<br />\n<br />\n克里斯惠蒂說，當地周四晚上，開始出現症狀，未接受病毒檢測，正在家中自我隔離。<br />\n<br />\n首相約翰遜及衛生大臣夏國賢，早前先後證實病毒測試呈陽性，兩人都在家中自我隔離。約翰遜在社交專頁發布影片，指自己有輕微病徵，包括發燒及持續咳嗽，經檢測證實染病，會在家中透過視像會議，繼續領導政府抗疫。<br />\n<br />\n白金漢宮表示，女王伊利沙伯二世對上一次與約翰遜見面，是在今個月11日。"},{"pid":"68c02c87115dc1d576cb99f205357aac9d4927c4","tid":1946792,"uid":194869,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-28T00:14:59.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fc6a6dee35e4ecb89ff8776452b03b52000b394d","tid":1946792,"uid":79563,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-28T00:15:49.000Z","msg":"入去欣賞一吓1120個青山派智力既ON<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />:<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1930886/page/1\" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1930886/page/1</a>"},{"pid":"7ac2f32d70905eae4678ce4315dd9ff9cd1bb8f5","tid":1946792,"uid":79563,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-28T00:17:27.000Z","msg":"成班都肺炎上腦：<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://i.postimg.cc/3xQfRD4Y/1.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.postimg.cc%2F3xQfRD4Y%2F1.jpg&h=79ca5f4d&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"34